{"tid":434196,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"路邊撿鹽　一家4口「手腳發黑」險滅門","createTime":"2017-10-13T05:00:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T03:32:39.000Z","uid":150685,"like":466,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd0bd6d742439500ec55d6e5dcf1c61257afb7a","tid":434196,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2853/d2853578.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2853%2Fd2853578.jpg&h=c7ce6097&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國浙江省溫州樂清市一名楊姓男子，日前逛菜市場時，在路邊意外撿到一包「鹽」，他舔一舔確認有鹹味，決定把它帶回家炒菜，不料一家四口吃飽飯後陸續出現頭暈嘔吐、四肢發黑症狀，送醫後診斷為勿食工業用的「亞硝酸鹽」，所幸4人經急救後暫時沒有生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n根據《錢江晚報》報導，樂清某醫院急診室10月2日下午3時半收治了4名病人（2男2女），均有頭暈、嘔吐、四肢發黑症狀，甚至連嘴唇和舌頭都發黑，外表看起來十分可怕。其中楊姓男子症狀最嚴重，已經開始出現呼吸困難。<br />\n<br />\n院方原本以為是食物中毒，詳細詢問後才得知，楊男當天上午到菜市場時，路過一間沒開門的熟食店，發現店外掉落一袋鹽，他舔了一下發現是鹹的，決定帶回家炒菜，當天中午就用這袋鹽做了魚和豆腐，不料一家四口吃完後都相繼不適。<br />\n<br />\n經詳細檢查後，發現4人是誤食工業用的「亞硝酸鹽」，4名患者體內高鐵紅蛋白濃度明顯偏高，遠超過正常值的30倍，氧分壓卻只有30 mmHg，低於正常值83~108 mmHg。醫師表示，這代表4人病況嚴重，且由於誤食亞硝酸鹽已過了一段時間，無法洗胃治療，只能透過特殊解毒劑解毒，所幸4人目前均已脫離險境。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，相較於食用鹽，亞硝酸鹽顏色較黃，一旦勿食多在30分鐘至3小時內發病，會導致中樞神經損害，進而引發呼吸困難、循環衰竭、昏迷等，口服0.2~0.5克就會中毒，1~2克就可能致死。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171012/1029659.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20171012%2F1029659.htm&d=jbAUhHU3jRu91SjTUorCAgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=f6aec388\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20171012/1029659.htm</a>"},{"pid":"40853756050288a8ce7ed195a9d8fd45a508c6fd","tid":434196,"uid":150685,"like":349,"dislike":0,"score":349,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一包鹽值幾多錢，仲要支那鹽"},{"pid":"d651e9b0001dfdcdf3f6b4be4d73a84337044cf9","tid":434196,"uid":30966,"like":405,"dislike":0,"score":405,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:02:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一包鹽值幾多錢，仲要支那鹽</blockquote><br />\n貴過條命"},{"pid":"ba5e7f0ab495c9ae840af8675a8d0763487fffdc","tid":434196,"uid":42188,"like":336,"dislike":4,"score":332,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:02:38.000Z","msg":"咁都死唔去<br />\n包工業鹽渣ga"},{"pid":"b90d155c2f92c9a4e1311d7b4b6c4fefd93d4f78","tid":434196,"uid":123224,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"強國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60afa59a76b79afed581a042bda03447bcbb9fcf","tid":434196,"uid":73,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:03:56.000Z","msg":"武裝式霸氣"},{"pid":"f46d0d4578d757936ee63d2bc852e8178ced39ee","tid":434196,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c1411a747e5e443ca699aa14e02261b4f60c04","tid":434196,"uid":9708,"like":292,"dislike":1,"score":291,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都死唔去<br />\n包工業鹽渣ga</blockquote><br />\n可能呢包都係溝左食鹽既假工業鹽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cb32a2770d3c4b7fc04bd4b8587bbb4313b9348","tid":434196,"uid":110832,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:05:05.000Z","msg":"民智未開嘅國家係咁<br />\n死多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0133ee4d795cfc9844decc4aad31f809b3f51e2","tid":434196,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:09:05.000Z","msg":"險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8848b9f1b94f987f50a2cee1de427807f9d9e504","tid":434196,"uid":5267,"like":242,"dislike":2,"score":240,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T05:09:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ab9a116c315052d66a29a47c5debeff774dcf50","tid":434196,"uid":136119,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201